<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Apollo" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Apollo,</orth> the famous God of ancient Greece: <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.328" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 328</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.2.79" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 2, 79</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.1.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 1, 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.4.15" default="NO" valid="yes">4, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.162" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 162</bibl>. God of music and song: <bibl n="shak. lll 4.3.343" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL IV, 3, 343</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.941" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 941</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 37.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.305" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 305</bibl>. of art and letters: <bibl n="shak. per 3.2.67" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. III, 2, 67</bibl>. of light and the sun (cf. <emph>Phoebus</emph>): <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 30</bibl>. of prophecy (by the Delphian oracle): <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.183" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 1, 183</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.3.200" default="NO" valid="yes">3, 200</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 14</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.117" default="NO" valid="yes">2, 117</bibl> sq. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 37</bibl>. In love with Daphne: <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.231" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 231</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 61.</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.1.101" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 1, 101</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>